            [
                "Into heaps – And what is this song, is it not a lament? Rather, it says “The Lord has spent His fury…” (Lamentations 4:11) And how did He spend it? “…and He has kindled a fire in Zion…” (ibid.) Therefore this is a song of rejoicing because He poured out His fury on wood and stones and did not make an end of His children."
            ]
